  "title": "Sales Executive – F&B / Indian Bar",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are an Indian bar specialising in authentic Karnataka (Bangalore-style) bar bites and small plates. We are seeking a Sales Executive to support business growth by driving sales through corporate bookings, events, and partnerships.</p><p>This role focuses on generating revenue, managing client relationships, and promoting the restaurant’s offerings to new and existing customers.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><p><p>Identify and develop new sales opportunities, including group bookings and events</p></p><p><p>Manage enquiries related to reservations, private events, and corporate functions</p></p><p><p>Build and maintain relationships with corporate clients and partners</p></p><p><p>Promote the restaurant’s food and beverage offerings to increase sales</p></p><p><p>Prepare sales proposals, quotations, and follow up on enquiries</p></p><p><p>Coordinate with operations and kitchen teams to ensure smooth event execution</p></p><p><p>Track sales performance and maintain accurate records of bookings</p></p><p><p>Support marketing initiatives and promotional activities</p></p></p><h3>Job Requirements</h3><p><p><p>Minimum 2–4 years of relevant sales experience, preferably in F&B or hospitality</p></p><p><p>Strong communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills</p></p><p><p>Customer-focused and results-driven mindset</p></p><p><p>Ability to work independently and manage multiple enquiries</p></p><p><p>Comfortable interacting with clients and stakeholders</p></p><p><p>Basic computer skills for reporting and coordination</p></p></p>",
